{"id":537,"date":"2022-11-18T23:09:37","date_gmt":"2022-11-18T23:09:37","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/prowler.com\/?p=537"},"modified":"2022-11-18T23:09:38","modified_gmt":"2022-11-18T23:09:38","slug":"scan-complete-notifications-updated","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/prowler.com\/blog\/scan-complete-notifications-updated\/","title":{"rendered":"Scan Complete Notifications Updated"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>We&#8217;ve updated the <strong>CosmicArmorPro<\/strong> scan complete notification to include a summary of the audit findings. This gives users a quick \u2018at-a-glance\u2019 summary of how their systems are operating, which can easily be shared with other teams if escalation is needed.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/scan-complete-email-smaller-1-707x1024.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-542\" width=\"384\" height=\"556\" srcset=\"https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/scan-complete-email-smaller-1-707x1024.png 707w, https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/scan-complete-email-smaller-1-207x300.png 207w, https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/scan-complete-email-smaller-1-768x1112.png 768w, https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/scan-complete-email-smaller-1-62x90.png 62w, https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/scan-complete-email-smaller-1-90x130.png 90w, https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/scan-complete-email-smaller-1-900x1303.png 900w, https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/scan-complete-email-smaller-1-800x1158.png 800w, https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/scan-complete-email-smaller-1-700x1013.png 700w, https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/scan-complete-email-smaller-1-600x869.png 600w, https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/scan-complete-email-smaller-1-500x724.png 500w, https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/scan-complete-email-smaller-1-400x579.png 400w, https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/scan-complete-email-smaller-1-300x434.png 300w, https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/scan-complete-email-smaller-1-200x290.png 200w, https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/scan-complete-email-smaller-1-100x145.png 100w, https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/scan-complete-email-smaller-1.png 947w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 384px) 100vw, 384px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>To enable the scan complete e-mail notifications, go to <a href=\"https:\/\/app.prowler.pro\/app\/settings\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><strong>https:\/\/app.prowler.pro\/app\/settings<\/strong><\/a> and click the <strong>Send email as scans are completed <\/strong>checkbox.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/email-notifications-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-543\" width=\"387\" height=\"251\" srcset=\"https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/email-notifications-1.png 1024w, https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/email-notifications-1-300x196.png 300w, https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/email-notifications-1-768x501.png 768w, https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/email-notifications-1-90x59.png 90w, https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/email-notifications-1-138x90.png 138w, https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/email-notifications-1-1000x652.png 1000w, https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/email-notifications-1-900x587.png 900w, https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/email-notifications-1-600x391.png 600w, https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/email-notifications-1-500x326.png 500w, https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/email-notifications-1-200x130.png 200w, https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/email-notifications-1-100x65.png 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 387px) 100vw, 387px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>For the latest<strong> CosmicArmorPro<\/str